Answer.feedback: I feel like I selected a lot of sentences, but all of them feel vital. Also I'm picking sentences which fit into the grand narrative of all of these HITs, not just this one. I don't know if I should be doing that or not, but I expect that's what Turkers will consciously or unconsciously do as well.
